{"tid":2129400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食肆明天起禁堂食　業界料生意將大跌","createTime":"2020-07-28T14:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T14:52:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c9a3cc2e34b115c3e9a2322b79abe9f4999ecc","tid":2129400,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540418-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540418-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=c6d4ad87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540418-20200728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6564e115\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540418-20200728.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n食肆明日起全面禁止堂食，部分市民今日中午，都把握最後機會，光顧食肆堂食，部分食客坦言，新措施實施後會有不便。<br />\n<br />\n香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和估計，會有多500間食肆暫停營業，他擔心若措施維持至8月，業界整體生意額會下跌80%，損失約70億元。"},{"pid":"4d0f059cc9420f5cdb029c5d156273606754f563","tid":2129400,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"大家要開始準備幫趁黃店"},{"pid":"b56b011f05fe8e2d64734c10626de38dccf6a5c1","tid":2129400,"uid":364012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0d09c0ca265f8c8b07cc0ccf85f6b57f39734e","tid":2129400,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會唔記得啲人話: 哇 d暴從搞亂香港, 搞到啲生意仲衰過沙士"},{"pid":"cf50784ec9450974cb78fda97b17fd802f74be26","tid":2129400,"uid":112935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0d09c0ca265f8c8b07cc0ccf85f6b57f39734e","tid":2129400,"uid":193364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會唔記得啲人話: